adjectives.description: directorial (comparative more directorial, superlative most directorial)

entries.meaning: Of or pertaining to a director
examples: The Seventies, that most directorial of decades.

entries.meaning: Of or pertaining to administration or to a directorate
examples: After very warm debates, the result was, that the directorial minister of Mentz should make the strongest possible representations to the Emperor's principal commissary.
